Sid Burston https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sid_Burston 0 Sid Burston is an American actor who has performed in over forty stage plays and fourteen national tours. He has played numerous lead and supporting roles in film and television. Burston release his debut gospel album Get Thee Behind Me in 1997.
